{"tid":1126251,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手樓價再漲1.6% 三大指數齊升11周","createTime":"2019-04-26T09:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T11:27:13.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"396e0d8ce4dfa2e2b59fa6da1f1144df2d5ac139","tid":1126251,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"反映二手樓價的中原城市領先指數(CCL)最新報183.19點，按周升1.56%。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數(CCL Mass)報185.47點，按周升1.12%。CCL(中小型單位)報183.14點，按周升1.19%。<br />\n<br />\n三大整體指數齊升11周，為102周以來首見，上一次出現是2017年5月。CCL Mass累升8.55%，CCL(中小型單位)升8.08%，CCL升7.79%。另外，CCL(大型單位)最新報183.43點，按周升3.52%，升幅為56周最大。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，新春後樓價正式展開連升，CCL持續向上挑戰歷史高位。四大整體指數中，以CCL(大型單位)最接近自己歷史高位，相差2.54%。 CCL、CCL Mass及CCL(中小型單位)分別相差2.89%、3.24%及3.32%。他相信樓價升勢持續，今年中CCL將重返188.64點歷史高位。<br />\n<br />\n四區樓價方面，港九市區樓價表現持續突出。九龍CCL Mass最新報182.88點，按周升1.22%，連升10周共10.4%，創該區歷史最長連升。港島CCL Mass報192.59點，按周升0.98%，連升六周共7.81%，是2012年3月後最長連升。港九兩區齊升六周，平歷史最長齊升紀錄，上一次出現是2004年2月。<br />\n<br />\n新界東CCL Mass報192.93點，按周升3.06%，升幅是107周最大。新界西CCL Mass報165.11點，按周跌0.23%。<br />\n<br />\n四區指數中，港九兩區有望率先重返歷史高位，現時港島CCL Mass相差2.73%、九龍CCL Mass相差3.09%。而新界西CCL Mass及新界東CCL Mass分別相差6.71%及7.61%。🤦&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"78f9333dad0ec62bd6ed860da9e54a676d0c5bcc","tid":1126251,"uid":226177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"蓋清你想換樓?"},{"pid":"55ab8c5173d17ff9066e1c8e84cda6c2fc0a6cd0","tid":1126251,"uid":100965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"蓋清住邊頭"},{"pid":"57efd582b047bffb4f2ab0b34c9399ba81d82b72","tid":1126251,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ab8c5173d17ff9066e1c8e84cda6c2fc0a6cd0","tid":1126251,"uid":100965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"蓋清住邊頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"元朗"},{"pid":"cb852d3d7cff146b11ed28d6d329f876ca0612eb","tid":1126251,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"真 ？ midtown 天池屋ok ?"},{"pid":"0f275bb5fd43e26c2cea43812a8068625219f3cc","tid":1126251,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"真係重&rdquo;爆&rdquo;緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d54fb740713fddea75117039e171c3a07faa851","tid":1126251,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkb4aJN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkkb4aJN.png&h=17a891fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55ffe91cc323399273babde977574c919f1cd437","tid":1126251,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/Mr1ZHQPoF5E/mqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FMr1ZHQPoF5E%2Fmqdefault.jpg&h=0e4ed359&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9d61c86061df1a2a406f909d19589f26405a53d","tid":1126251,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"抹屎儿：又中"}]}